You are sitting South and playing Bergen Raises after a takeout double.|
pg| ***** 39 ***** |


NT||lb|*bWhat would you bid?^^2h|mb|2h|nt|^b@2
2@H is the correct bid even if you are playing Bergen Raises. You ignore the double. It is the same bid as in the constructive bidding.|
PG| ***** 41 ***** |


