^b@2The correct bid is 3@C if playing Regular Bergen|mb|3c|
PG| ***** 44 ***** |


ub||
pg| ***** 45 ***** |


at| and if playing Reverse Bergen the bid is 3@D.|mb|3D|
pg| ***** 46 ***** |


ub||
